#: ../../../../HOWTO_RELEASE.rst:32
msgid "**OS X**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../HOWTO_RELEASE.rst:34
msgid ""
"OS X versions >= 10.9 are supported, for Python version support see :ref:"
"`NEP 29 <NEP29>`. We build binary wheels for OSX that are compatible with "
"Python.org Python, system Python, homebrew and macports - see this `OSX "
"wheel building summary <https://github.com/MacPython/wiki/wiki/Spinning-"
"wheels>`_ for details."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../HOWTO_RELEASE.rst:40
msgid "**Windows**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../HOWTO_RELEASE.rst:42
msgid ""
"We build 32- and 64-bit wheels on Windows. Windows 7, 8 and 10 are "
"supported. We build NumPy using the `mingw-w64 toolchain`_, `cibuildwheels`_ "
"and GitHub actions."
