#: ../../../../HOWTO_RELEASE.rst:48
msgid "**Linux**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../HOWTO_RELEASE.rst:50
msgid ""
"We build and ship `manylinux2014 <https://www.python.org/dev/peps/"
